ğŸ¯ Goal: Understand how long an attacker could stay unnoticed â€” so that you can suggest better protection.

> ğŸ’¡ (As an ethical hacker, you donâ€™t actually do damage â€” you just test how possible it is.)

### 5ï¸âƒ£ **Clearing Tracks (Covering Your Trail)**

